name: Experiment Or Die #48
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. I've always been in love with the ocean and surf culture despite the fact that I've only been surfing once and I was absolutely terrible. I did grow up in the suburbs of upstate NY so didn't have much opportunity to surf growing up and as an adult I was really out of shape when I did try. It is VERY hard, and tiring. I thought I was gonna drown. That feeling is how I can often feel in a new space like crypto especially when you have doubts about your work. But you need to just keep on being yourself and eventually you will reach the right people. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
